data.text:
Whether you require 24/7 live-in care or just a bit of help on a daily basis, Henley Care can provide a personalised care package tailored to your needs. Our CQC-regulated carers and nurses deliver the highest quality care services across Berkshire, Hampshire, Oxfordshire, and West London.

Elder is an award winning care provider that can help you keep the life you know, all while getting the care you need.

For over 15 years, Promedica24 have been providing live-in home care to people who prefer not to move to a residential care home.
